description:

start off with the gameboys all DMG

Grey - £17
Yellow - £20
Green/Red/Blue - £30
Black/Transparent - £40
White £100

or if you want a mixed front and back or something else its open for negotiation.

backlight modification colours blue,green,yellow,white,red) - £25
purple/pink backlights - £35
different coloured buttons - £10
Pro sound Mod - £20
Replaced screen cover (gold/silver/play loud chip-tune) - £10.


gameboys can take upto 3 weeks to be completed (however usually under a week) so best emailing us and sorting out the payment etc that way.

name: Gameboy Arduinoboy Kit / PCB, Back In STOCK
description:
PCB's still available This is Nearly everything required to build a fully functional arduinoboy. this with the instructional .pdf found and MORE INFO on this product please Click Here.

This kit contains :- 1 x MEOW Arduinoboy PCB 1 x ATMEGA168 chip with latest arduinoboy software on it. (can be updated with an arduino or the serial ports) 1 x 28DIP IC socket 1 x 6n138 Optoisolator 1 x 8DIP IC socket 8 x 1K resistor 4 x 220 OHM resistor 2 x 270 OHM resistor 4 x 10k resistor 1 x 1uf electrolytic cap 1 x 1n48 diode 1 x 0.1uf ceramic cap (for serial in) 5 x Super bright Pink LED's 1 x Super bright Green LED 1 x 16MHz Resonator 1 x momentary Tactile switch 1 x Push button 1 x Toggle switch 1 x 7805 Regulator 2 x 5pin DIN socket (pcb or Panel Mount) 1 x 9v Battery Clip 3 x strands of equipment wire. it does NOT contain the enclosure above. The PCB and arduinoboy ATMEGA CHIP also comes with a 28 DIP socket for the chip. requires Electrical experience. a soldering iron etc. dispatched within 4 days.

All polaroids are one off, there is no way to replicate them, and taking polaroids now a days is quite an expensive commodity.

all taken and modified by S.Battle.

All are individually numbered and as more are done the numbers will go up, at the minute there are only 120.

on receiving the polaroids that hadnt sold yet from the polaroid exhibition in amsterdam they are now up for you guys.


you will receive the polaroid well packaged.
